{"id":769350,"title":"开篇词｜TypeScript 高手修炼指南","content":"<p>课程GitHub仓库（用于获取课程代码、下载课件）：<a href=\"https://github.com/aimingoo/jike2\">https://github.com/aimingoo/jike2</a></p>","comments":[{"had_liked":false,"id":390641,"user_name":"听水的湖","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c3","uid":1501385,"ip_address":"北京","ucode":"B1759F90165D81","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/16/e8/c9/59bcd490.jpg","comment_is_top":true,"comment_ctime":1715844612,"is_pvip":false,"replies":null,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":2,"product_id":100761001,"comment_content":"课程 GitHub 仓库（用于获取课程代码、下载课件）：https:&#47;&#47;github.com&#47;aimingoo&#47;jike2\n微信添加拉群小助手StuQ2017R2，回复“重学”即可加入课程交流群。","like_count":0},{"had_liked":false,"id":389946,"user_name":"杜森垚","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c3","uid":1230301,"ip_address":"北京","ucode":"71DEA59348CE09","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/12/c5/dd/5a482cab.jpg","comment_is_top":true,"comment_ctime":1713953104,"is_pvip":false,"replies":[{"id":141866,"content":"你好，谢谢关注😄\n课程是面向最新版本的TypeScript 5.x来讲述的。但是考虑到对知识结构的对齐，在讲述过程中对TypeScript 3.x及更早版本的特性不单独说明版本号。这是因为TS3.8已经对齐到了ES2020规范，并且包含了顶层await和空值检查等常用的高级特性，而TS3.9只有少量的优化改进。所有只有当某种特性是从TS4.x开始具备的，那么我才会在课程中明确指出这种特性引用的时间以及它需要解决的问题。\n基本上来说，所有新特性都会讲到。许多时候我甚至会指出某些只在release notes才有的知识点，因为这可能都还没更新到官方文档中去。","user_name":"作者回复","user_name_real":"编辑","uid":1521669,"ctime":1713962221,"ip_address":"河南","comment_id":389946,"utype":1}],"discussion_count":1,"race_medal":0,"score":2,"product_id":100761001,"comment_content":"这个课程使用的typescript版本是多少","like_count":1,"discussions":[{"author":{"id":1521669,"avatar":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/17/38/05/7beecd5d.jpg","nickname":"Aiming","note":"","ucode":"66292B32F9960A","race_medal":0,"user_type":2,"is_pvip":false},"reply_author":{"id":0,"avatar":"","nickname":"","note":"","ucode":"","race_medal":0,"user_type":1,"is_pvip":false},"discussion":{"id":642987,"discussion_content":"你好，谢谢关注😄\n课程是面向最新版本的TypeScr